text: Frédérique Massat (born January 14, 1964) was a member of the National Assembly of France. She represented the Ariège department, and is a member of the Socialist, Radical, Citizen and Miscellaneous Left. ==References== *National Assembly of France profile Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Women members of the National Assembly (France) Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:21st-century French women politicians
title: Frédérique Massat
